                                Another way of making a request is by using the expression Is it #[strong alright if...?]#[br]
                            blockquote #[strong • Eg:] Is it alright if I leave early today? It’s just that I’m not feeling very well.
                            div(class="row")
                                .col.xs6.mt20: div(class="row row-flex align-items-center justify-center")
                                    img(src="unit_2/module_8/assets/images/act_13_1.png" alt="" class="u-responsive-img m-a")
